

#### Bindings
## Buttons
Button   Control    1    cursor      toggle
Button   Control    2    quit
Button   Control    3    follow
Button   Shift      1    pan
Button   Shift      2    redraw      normal
Button   Shift      3    zoom
Button              1    next
Button              2    sorter      toggle
Button              3    prev
Button              4    history     back
Button              5    history     forward
## Keys
Key      Control    q    quit
Key      Control    f    fullscreen
